{"tid":354260,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"小朋友急尿係街邊痾有咩問題","createTime":"2017-08-10T09:35:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-11T12:12:04.000Z","uid":17521,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2a2535f1c213e4dce6d2d02cb073f0f757e22e00","tid":354260,"uid":17521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T09:35:38.000Z","msg":"屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好撚大問題呀<br />\n<br />\n今日係西九行出黎，見到有個阿媽抱住個細路仲以為佢咁撚有母愛抱住個𡃁仔飲水。<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母，行近啲睇原來對住條馬路痾尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 九秒九攞起部相機廢撚事佢唔認數。影完就已經好聲好氣同佢講西九𥚃面其實有廁所，唔駛係正人地個門口痾。佢就講左兩聲sor諗住走。<br />\n<br />\n我問佢有冇水沖下個地下，佢話冇，我叫佢即刻買枝沖都好。佢求鳩其應左我，之後去左等紅綠燈。我跟住佢過馬路，經過一間七仔，問佢做乜鳩唔買呀之類嘅野，佢就發老皮話返屋企攞(信佢老母咩)。<br />\n<br />\n成件事嘅重點係咩？如果係講支那文，我都仲覺得有可能發生。條臭閪講純正廣東話架，廣東話呀！仲識駁返我呀。究竟香港人質素係咪每況愈下緊？係咪步向緊支那嘅步伐....<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最大問題係冇一個香港人理呀，大家睇到係好似見慣不怪咁。其實香港係咪真係病得咁嚴重？小學生唔講廣東話，廢老爭位坐 上網批鬥人。以為政治問題已經搞到一團糟，原來民生都係咁<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/10/173528_45e14d45671ebd685cf2dcb6c5feb8c4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F10%2F173528_45e14d45671ebd685cf2dcb6c5feb8c4.jpg&h=69eccf6f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ee29a8a1052e79a062e097f343256a8a879a76fb","tid":354260,"uid":38909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T09:36:44.000Z","msg":"連印度人都睇唔過眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5994bd368a06349cbc8a1287f413f68c4e6dd63","tid":354260,"uid":17521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T09:38:23.000Z","msg":"點解成班香港人要扮瞓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bca6b1ce25ab012966aaec2b86b76d2e307a9e4","tid":354260,"uid":17521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T09:49:24.000Z","msg":"寵物台冇人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a78cccb0242aa84ea98e60773b04ab3436bd630","tid":354260,"uid":17521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T15:54:49.000Z","msg":"原來冇人睇寵物台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be291e530953e51f74ca9b01ae37ab6d58d28313","tid":354260,"uid":103186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T19:10:24.000Z","msg":"上樑不正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0952f7d8b35b9ab515f636942a822e35054b77fe","tid":354260,"uid":17425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T20:26:05.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母嘛"},{"pid":"d0cd3c88ee51f63a435ae88631faf88309b5857c","tid":354260,"uid":17521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T04:30:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌佢老母嘛</blockquote><br />\n我有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但成班港豬望住我，好似當我癲佬咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbfebe0ab7d2d6822f807532e311452035810007","tid":354260,"uid":2758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T09:06:46.000Z","msg":"狗先會隨街痾屎痾尿"},{"pid":"2b175fd99c2fa7d5e611fa6c9974855eed05e27c","tid":354260,"uid":17521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T09:55:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>狗先會隨街痾屎痾尿</blockquote><br />\n所以先放寵物台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但原來冇人睇"},{"pid":"8a280430c7f3d2a1ff24dc8a6d9e1b63fc4d184b","tid":354260,"uid":59567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T09:57:30.000Z","msg":"狗都係咁支那畜也可以吧"},{"pid":"9024ad14de95cd4b35da9c1e1239b86adcc9c94e","tid":354260,"uid":17521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T12:12:04.000Z","msg":"當你見到睇到嘅人扮睇唔到 先係你對香港最失望嘅地方"}]}